lyrics:
Ho, haul away, yo-ho!
We'll sail with Ahmed, to and fro,
Through storm and calm, we'll bravely go,
For Ahmed, the pirate, we follow!

(Verse 1)
From the shores of Somalia, Ahmed did rise,
With a gleam in his eye and a sword by his side.
A captain bold, on the open sea,
His flag unfurled, wild and free!
